{"tid":2048961,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被問特朗普為開路驅散示威者　加總理語塞21秒","createTime":"2020-06-03T06:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T07:41:02.000Z","uid":171273,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"11cb965e585cae974f9110532000f0ee6b087d35","tid":2048961,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:42:45.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國總統特朗普為了由白宮前往附近的聖約翰教堂拍照而驅散示威群眾，有記者要求加拿大總理杜魯多回應時，他一度沉默長達21秒。<br />\n<br />\n杜魯多的沉默長達21秒，有傳媒形容一向反應快的他，今次似乎有點不知所措，在沉默期間似乎努力思索如何回應，最後杜魯多表示，所有人看到美國發生的事都感到驚愕，但無提及特朗普的名字。<br />\n<br />\n杜魯多之後又提到加拿大都有種族歧視問題，呼籲所有人聯手對抗。<br />\n<br />\n有指杜魯多一向小心避免批評特朗普，目前加拿大有七成半的貨品都出口到美國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=393147&amp;fbclid=IwAR0RJm8DDYFe5cV-Uln_JFG0slrBK0ESY9BNkLJtzpaihNwXD7cKiwXbNjE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393147%26fbclid%3DIwAR0RJm8DDYFe5cV-Uln_JFG0slrBK0ESY9BNkLJtzpaihNwXD7cKiwXbNjE&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgbTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=cfcf304f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393147%26fbclid%3DIwAR0RJm8DDYFe5cV-Uln_JFG0slrBK0ESY9BNkLJtzpaihNwXD7cKiwXbNjE&h=9b3d24f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=393147&amp;fbclid=IwAR0RJm8DDYFe5cV-Uln_JFG0slrBK0ESY9BNkLJtzpaihNwXD7cKiwXbNjE</a><br />\n<br />\n條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b84724dc4d75cb6310fcb5116eb2de7b33a1a93","tid":2048961,"uid":26752,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:45:13.000Z","msg":"冇腦多：大佬叫到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我呢d做契弟既邊有得話事啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac4dc938098cf07a135